summary: The Airbus A330 is a large passenger airplane. It was made to be a bigger version of the Airbus A300. The A330 and the Airbus A340 were designed together and share many parts. The A330 has two engines and three wheels on its main landing gear. It can fly very far, carrying many passengers. There are different types of A330s, like the A330-200 and A330-300. The A330neo is a newer version with better engines and fuel efficiency. Delta Air Lines has the most A330s. Over 1,800 A330s have been ordered, making it a popular choice for airlines.
title: Airbus A330
